column29: Four-day old Arabidopsis thaliana Col-0 or ztl-3 mutants seedlings grown on MS plate under 12 h white light of 70 to 100 micro mol s-1 m-2 / 12 h dark conditions (LD) were transferred to 96-well plates (136101 Nunc MicroWell White plate, Thermo Fisher Scientific) with a 6 mm diameter dropper. Seedlings were treated with 20 micro L of MS liquid containing 2% (w/v) sucrose and 5% DMSO, and kept under LD for 2 days. Seedlings were harvested at ZT18.
